roBooNE optical units. While the information shown\nhere is MicroBooNE specific, the approach to the model and the collection of\nsimulation parameters will be widely applicable to many liquid-argon-based\nlight collection systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Nov 2017 16:39:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Nov 2017 17:27:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 5 Mar 2018 15:28:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-06"}
