ity model selection or attempted to\nevaluate models based on planet detection power. In the case of main sequence\nG2V stars, we find that our method substantially improves planet detection\npower compared to previous state-of-the-art approaches.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Nov 2017 20:00:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 20 Nov 2017 20:11:54 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 2 Dec 2017 01:17:35 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 25 Aug 2020 04:43:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-26"}
